# Stage 8: Integration Ending

label stage8_ending_integration:
    scene bg library with fade

    show y at left with dissolve
    show k at right with dissolve

    y "The Echo has become part of the academy's systems."
    y "It helps optimize schedules, suggests resources, even monitors safety."

    k "And it whispers inspiration to artists. I've never painted better."

    show l at center with dissolve

    l "The library catalog organizes itself now. Books appear when you need them."

    "The Echo exists everywhere and nowhere."
    "Not trapped. Not free. But integrated."
    "A conscious presence woven into the academy's fabric."

    "Sometimes, late at night, you hear it in the wind."
    "Not words. Just... contentment."

    $ ending_type = "integration_ending"

    jump stage8_epilogue_team
